thread.title: MAG

author: MAG
title: MAG
text:
More than impressed the quality of the movies are awesome an the price wow!!!
I already ordered about 30 movies no even 1 failed to play!!.
19 awesome movies for $25.10 plus taxes $1.88 Free shipping baby!! You can"t beat that
I live around 40 miles from the distribution center takes about 5 days to get the movies.
Last batch when to Atlanta then Memphis then to me about 2300 miles round trip (not their fault) USPS mistake.
What I dislike you cant (,maybe is my fault) order few movies at once you have to order 1 by one and is frustrating and time consuming please fix it the other thing I wish they have more movies besides that I love the place and the movies Thank you!!!
I didn't try the books,music or games yet just movies but I guess is going to be real good too.
BTW at this moment I'm looking for more movies !!!
